table!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"style\":{\"layout\":[]}} -->\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":10,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"wide\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pexels-jefriwibawa-1387037-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"},\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"0\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center is-style-asterisk\">Get all of the party details here!</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fit\",\"flexSize\":null}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Our comprehensive suite of professional services caters to a diverse clientele, ranging from homeowners to commercial developers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"40%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-asterisk\"><a href=\"/schedule/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"25\">Itinerary</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join us for a day of sun, fun, and unforgettable moments as we celebrate Alex’s 25th birthday with friends, laughter, and a packed schedule of beachside activities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:image {\"lightbox\":{\"enabled\":false},\"id\":12,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded\"><a href=\"/schedule/\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pexels-nubikini-386025-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:image {\"lightbox\":{\"enabled\":false},\"id\":45,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"custom\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded\"><a href=\"/venue/\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pexels-quang-nguyen-vinh-222549-3355734-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-45\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"40%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-asterisk\"><a href=\"/venue/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"30\">Venue</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Set against the stunning backdrop of Golden Sands Shore, our beach venue is the perfect place to relax, reconnect, and make new memories with Alex and friends.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"40%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"is-style-asterisk\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-asterisk\"><a href=\"#\">Guest Community Portal</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stay connected before, during, and after the party in our community portal, where you can share photos, memories, and messages with Alex and the entire crew.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"50%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":16,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pexels-askar-abayev-5638829-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Testimonial\"},\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|60\"},\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}},\"backgroundColor\":\"contrast\",\"textColor\":\"base\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-base-color has-contrast-background-color has-text-color has-background\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.2\"}},\"textColor\":\"base\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\",\"fontFamily\":\"heading\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-base-color has-text-color has-heading-font-family has-x-large-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.2\"><em>\"Alex’s parties are always legendary, but this one is going to be next-level! The beach, the bonfire, and all of us reunited—what more could we ask for?\"</em><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-615ed285-7fff-ec42-eae1-01d915b6e39f\"></span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Testimonial source\"},\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"0\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|10\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);margin-bottom:0\">Taylor</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\"}},\"textColor\":\"contrast-3\",\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-contrast-3-color has-text-color has-small-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:300\">Master of Party Vibes &amp; Head of Bonfire Toast Management</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"},\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"wide\",\"style\":{\"typography\":