(69, 1, '2024-08-02 18:19:00', '2024-08-02 18:19:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hello party people!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We’re just a few weeks away from Alex’s big 2-5 celebration, and we’ve got some exciting updates to share with you! 🎉</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First off, we’re thrilled to announce a couple of&nbsp;<strong>special surprises</strong>&nbsp;that we’ve added to the itinerary:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Live Music at the Bonfire:</strong> We’ve arranged for a live acoustic performance during the bonfire session! Get ready to sing along to some of Alex’s favorite tunes under the stars.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Personalized Party Favors:</strong> We’re putting together some fun, personalized party favors for each of you to take home as a memento of the day. Trust us—you’ll love them!</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A few things to keep in mind:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Group Photo:</strong> The group photo is happening at 5:00 PM sharp. Make sure you’re there—this is one picture you won’t want to miss!</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Weather Watch:</strong> The forecast looks sunny, but just in case, keep an eye out for any weather updates. We’ll let you know if anything changes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We’re so excited to see everyone and celebrate the amazing person Alex is. Get ready for a day full of fun, friends, and fantastic memories!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stay tuned for more updates, and see you soon at Golden Sands Shore!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Best,<br>Emily<