(73, 1, '2024-09-03 18:28:02', '2024-09-03 18:28:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here’s some engaging text for the “Venue” page:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Venue: Celebrate at Golden Sands Shore</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to <strong>Golden Sands Shore</strong>—the perfect backdrop for Alex’s 25th birthday celebration! 🌊✨</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Imagine a day filled with sunshine, gentle ocean breezes, and the sound of waves crashing on the shore as you gather with friends to celebrate Alex’s big milestone. Golden Sands Shore isn’t just any beach—it’s a slice of paradise where every corner is a photo-worthy moment waiting to happen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether you’re lounging under a beach umbrella, playing a friendly game of volleyball, or enjoying a sunset dinner by the water, this beach has something for everyone. As the day turns to night, we’ll light up the bonfire and continue the festivities under a starry sky, with the ocean as our soundtrack.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Why Golden Sands Shore is Perfect:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Breathtaking Views:</strong> With its golden sands, clear blue waters, and stunning sunsets, this beach is the ultimate spot for an unforgettable celebration.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Plenty of Space:</strong> Whether you want to join in on the beach games or find a quiet spot to relax and catch up, there’s room for everyone.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Convenient Location:</strong> Located just [X] minutes from [Nearest Tow