(206, 1, '2025-04-25 17:54:15', '2025-04-25 17:54:15', '<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>When\'s this shindig happening?</strong> (What time does the party start and end?)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>We\'re kicking off at 2:00 PM sharp (beach time = fashionably late is totally fine) and partying until the sun gives up and goes to bed, around 7:30 PM. No one\'s taking attendance, so show up whenever your beach body is ready!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>What\'s the beach party survival kit?</strong> (What should I bring?)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Bring sunscreen (unless you\'re going for the lobster look), a towel (for sitting, not crying), and swimwear (skinny dipping is frowned upon). We\'ve got the burgers, drinks, and wobbly beach chairs covered!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>Where do I park my chariot?</strong> (or: Is there parking available?)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>There\'s a magical parking lot right by the beach entrance. Pro tip: Early birds get the spots, late birds get the 10-minute hike from the overflow lot. Choose your adventure!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>Can I bring my significant other, work bestie, or emotional support person?</strong> (aka: \"Can I bring a plus-one?\")</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>YES! The more the merrier! Just give us a heads up so we don\'t run out of hot dogs. We draw the line at bringing your ex though – this is a party, not a reality show.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>Will I need to hunt for my own food like a beach seagull?</strong> (aka: should we bring our own food and drinks? or can we?)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>We\'ve got you covered with enough food and drinks to feed a small army! But if you\'re picky, have special cravings, or just really love that one specific snack, bring it along. Got dietary restrictions? Give us a heads up so we don\'t accidentally feed you something your stomach will regret later.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>I don\'t eat meat. Will I starve?</strong> (or: Will there be vegetarian/vegan options?)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Fear not, herbivore friends! We\'ve got veggie burgers that don\'t taste like cardboard, grilled veggies that\'ll make carnivores question their ways, and enough fruit to start your own smoothie business.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>What if Mother Nature decides to crash the party with rain?</strong> </summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Rain or shine, we\'re beach-bound! We\'ve got a covered pavilion area where you can stay dry while still enjoying the ocean view. Plus, we\'re bringing rain-proof games, waterproof speakers for dance parties, and extra beach umbrellas. Think of it as \"extreme beach partying\" – because nothing stops Alex\'s birthday bash! (And let\'s be honest, dancing in the rain is kind of epic.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>Do I need to bring a gift for the birthday human?</strong> (aka: Alex)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Your beautiful face is present enough! But if you\'re feeling generous, Alex has an unhealthy obsession with board games and travel books. Or just bring a funny birthday card – bonus points if it makes us snort-laugh!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>What\'s the dress code? Ball gowns and tuxedos?</strong></summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Please, no! We\'re going full beach casual – think \"I woke up like this\" but make it cute. Light, breezy clothes are your friend, and YES bring that swimsuit! Don\'t forget sunscreen (lobster is not a good look) and sunglasses (squinting ruins photos). When the sun dips, you\'ll want a light jacket or blanket for the bonfire – s\'mores taste better when you\'re cozy!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>When\'s the mandatory \"let\'s pretend we all like each other\" group photo?</strong></summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>5:00 PM sharp! Be there or be forever cropped out of the memories. We\'re doing this proper Instagram-worthy style, so bring your best smile (or at least your best \"I\'m having fun\" face). This is the one photo Alex\'s mom will frame forever!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary><strong>Who do I call if I\'m lost/confused/having an existential crisis at (or before) the party?</strong> (or: contact info and what to do if you have questions)</summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p>Emily (Alex\'s sister and party superhero) is your go-to person at 888-888-8888. She\'s got answers to everything from \"Where\'s the bathroom?\" to \"Why are we all here?\" Save her number – she\'s basically party Google.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:details -->\n<details class=\"wp-block-details\"><summary></summary><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Type / to add a hidden block\"} -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details --></details>\n<!-- /wp:details -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Q: What\'s the real point of all this?</strong><br>A: Have. Fun. Period. This isn\'t just another beach day – it\'s Alex\'s quarter-century celebration! Come ready to laugh until your sides hurt, make memories that\'ll embarrass us in 10 years, and celebrate our friend in the most ridiculously awesome way possible. Bonus points if you start a conga line!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'F.A.Q.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-autosave-v1', '', '', '2025-04-25 17:54:15', '2025-04-25 17:54:15', '', 32, '/?p=206', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
