(211, 1, '2025-04-25 17:55:43', '2025-04-25 17:55:43', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":55,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Drinks-Burst-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-55\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Welcome Drinks &amp; Catch-Up</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;2:00 PM<br><br>Kick off the celebration with a refreshing drink at the beach bar as everyone arrives. It’s the perfect time to catch up, meet new friends, and soak in the sun. Don’t forget to grab your welcome drink and start mingling—let’s get this party started!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":57,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beach-Games-Photo-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-57\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beach Games &amp; Fun in the Sun</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;3:00 PM<br><br>Get ready for some friendly competition with beach volleyball, frisbee, and more! Whether you’re in it to win it or just want to have fun, there’s something for everyone. Bring your A-game, or just cheer on your friends from the sidelines with a drink in hand!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":58,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beach-Photography-Session-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-58\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Group Photo Session</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;5:00 PM<br><br>Let’s capture the moment with a group photo to remember Alex’s big day! Gather around as we snap a few shots with the ocean as our backdrop. Be sure to bring your best smile, and let’s create a keepsake that Alex will cherish forever.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":60,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Umutart-17461431-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-60\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sunset Dinner by the Shore</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Time:</strong>&nbsp;6:00 PM<br><br>As the sun begins to set, we’ll gather for a delicious dinner by the shore. Enjoy a meal with friends while taking in the stunning view, followed by a few toasts to celebrate Alex. This is the time to relax, enjoy, and reflect on all the good times we’ve shared.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-bl