(226, 13, '2025-04-25 19:23:03', '2025-04-25 19:23:03', 'Hey everyone! 👋 I\'m SO in for volleyball! Fair warning though - my serves are about as reliable as beach wifi, but I make up for it with enthusiasm and really loud cheering 😂\r\n\r\nI can play any position (badly) but I\'m best at not getting in the way. Who needs a team member that brings more spirit than skill? I promise to dive dramatically for every ball, even if I miss 90% of them!\r\n\r\nAlso, can we please have team names? I vote for \"Sandy Cheeks\" or \"Sets on the Beach\" 🏐🌊\r\n\r\nP.S. I\'ll bring extra sunscreen for my team because sunburned volleyball players are no fun!', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', '226', '', '', '2025-08-15 15:52:41', '2025-08-15 15:52:41', '', 217, '/forums/reply/226/', 1, 'reply', '', 0),
