(240, 18, '2025-06-11 17:52:21', '2025-06-11 17:52:21', 'Photography nerd reporting for duty! 📸\n\nI\'ve been thinking about our group photo setup and I have OPINIONS (shocking, I know). With that gorgeous ocean backdrop at 5 PM, we\'re going to have perfect golden hour lighting – this could be magazine-worthy if we play it right!\n\nHere are some pose ideas that won\'t make us look like awkward penguins:\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Classic tiered formation but everyone turns slightly toward the center</li>\n	<li>Walking toward camera in a loose line (candid vibes!)</li>\n	<li>Everyone jumping at the same time (yes, it\'s cliché but Alex will love it)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\nI\'m bringing my good camera AND a tripod, so we can get multiple angles. Also, I volunteer as tribute to take individual friend group shots throughout the day – consider me your personal party paparazzi!\n\nWho\'s brave enough to let me direct them for 30 seconds? I promise I won\'t be too bossy… okay, I might be a little bossy 😅', 'Group Photo Poses: Ideas to Make Us Look Cool', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'group-photo-poses-ideas-to-make-us-look-cool', '', '', '2025-06-13 15:28:04', '2025-06-13 15:28:04', '', 236, '/forums/topic/group-photo-poses-ideas-to-make-us-look-cool/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
