(253, 19, '2025-06-13 15:31:37', '2025-06-13 15:31:37', '<strong>Listen up frisbee fanatics! </strong>🥏\n\nI may be known for my dance moves, but don\'t sleep on my frisbee skills! I\'ve got surprisingly good hand-eye coordination (all those years of catching dance props finally paying off lol).\n\nI\'m hereby challenging EVERYONE to bring their A-game because Sofia\'s coming for that frisbee crown! Fair warning: I will be doing victory dances after every good throw, so prepare yourselves for some impromptu choreography on the beach 😂\n\nWho\'s ready to get schooled by someone who spends more time practicing pirouettes than frisbee throws? The trash talk starts NOW!\n\nBring it on, beach warriors! 💪', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '253', '', '', '2025-06-13 15:31:37', '2025-06-13 15:31:37', '', 220, '/forums/reply/253/', 1, 'reply', '', 0),
(254, 5, '2025-06-13 15:41:54', '2025-06-13 15:41:54', '<strong>Alright party people, the grill master has arrived!</strong> 🔥\n\nI\'m volunteering to handle ALL the grilling duties – and I mean ALL of it. I\'ve got my trusty portable grill, premium charcoal (none of that gas nonsense), and my secret spice blend that\'s been in the family for generations (<em>okay, I invented it last year, but it\'s still amazing</em>).\n\nHere\'s what I\'m bringing to the meat department:\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Burgers (beef AND turkey for variety)</li>\n	<li>Hot dogs (the good kind, not those mystery meat ones)</li>\n	<li>Marinated chicken skewers</li>\n	<li>Veggie burgers for our plant-based friends (yes, I know how to grill those too!)</li></ul>\n\nI\'ll also bring all the grilling tools, extra propane backup (just in case), and way too much aluminum foil.\nWhat I NEED from you all: buns, condiments, sides, and someone to keep me company at the grill! Fair warning – I will judge your burger-flipping technique if you try to \"help\" 😂\n\nWho\'s covering what? Let\'s get this coordination locked down!', 'Who\'s Bringing What? Potluck Coordination', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'whos-bringing-what-potluck-coordination', '', '', '2025-06-13 15:46:12', '2025-06-13 15:46:12', '', 234, '/forums/topic/whos-bringing-what-potluck-coordination/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
