(257, 8, '2025-06-13 15:50:51', '2025-06-13 15:50:51', 'Okay conspirators, we need to get ORGANIZED! 🕵️‍♀️\n\nI\'ve been thinking about Alex\'s surprise and I have a foolproof plan, but I need everyone\'s help to pull it off. What if we coordinate a surprise video montage from all the friends who couldn\'t make it? I can collect videos throughout the week and play it during dinner!\n\nAlso, I secretly reached out to Alex\'s mom and she\'s sending her favorite childhood photos for a \"25 Years of Alex\" slideshow. I\'m thinking we project it during the bonfire?\n\nI\'ve already made a shared folder (link in my profile) where everyone can upload photos and videos. Let\'s make this the most memorable surprise ever! Who\'s in?\n\nP.S. - I may have also ordered custom beach towels with embarrassing baby photos of Alex. Sorry not sorry! 😂', 'Top Secret Birthday Surprise Planning (DON\'T LET ALEX SEE THIS)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'top-secret-birthday-surprise-planning-dont-let-alex-see-this', '', '', '2025-06-13 15:50:51', '2025-06-13 15:50:51', '', 231, '/forums/topic/top-secret-birthday-surprise-planning-dont-let-alex-see-this/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
(258, 11, '2025-06-13 15:53:27', '2025-06-13 15:53:27', 'I\'ve been thinking about what story to share around the bonfire and I\'m torn between three options:\n\n<ol>\n	<li>The time Alex and I got lost hiking and ended up having a 3-hour philosophical debate about whether hot dogs are sandwiches (we still disagree)</li>\n	<li>That epic road trip where Alex\'s GPS died and we \"navigated by vibes\" for 200 miles</li>\n	<li>The night we stayed up until sunrise writing terrible song lyrics about our college professors</li></ol>\n\nI\'m leaning toward #2 because it perfectly captures Alex\'s \"everything will work out\" attitude that we all love!\n\nAnyone else practicing their stories? I volunteer to bring my guitar for some acoustic accompaniment if people want background music while they share. Nothing says \"meaningful bonfire moment\" like some gentle strumming!\n\nAlso, does anyone know if Alex still cries during emotional stories? Asking for a friend... 😂🎸\n\n<strong>What stories are you all planning to share?</strong>', 'Story circle prep time! 📖🔥', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'story-circle-prep-time-%f0%9f%93%96%f0%9f%94%a5', '', '', '2025-06-13 15:53:27', '2025-06-13 15:53:27', '', 238, '/forums/topic/story-circle-prep-time-%f0%9f%93%96%f0%9f%94%a5/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
(261, 13, '2025-06-13 16:00:08', '2025-06-13 16:00:08', 'Hey beach party squad! 🚗💨\n\nSo I may have gotten a little too excited about this party and completely forgot that my car is currently in the shop (don\'t ask about the parking meter incident... 🙈).\n\nI\'m looking for a ride from the downtown area and I promise I\'m an excellent passenger! I bring snacks, good playlists, and absolutely zero backseat driving. I can chip in for gas and I\'ll even throw in some of my famous homemade cookies as payment!\n\nBut this got me thinking - why don\'t we all coordinate carpools? It\'s better for the environment, saves money, AND gives us extra party time to catch up on the drive!\n\nDrop a comment if you:\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Need a ride (like moi!)</li>\n	<li>Have extra seats in your car</li>\n	<li>Want to split gas costs</li>\n	<li>Just want road trip buddies</li></ul>\n\nLet\'s turn the drive to Alex\'s party into part of the celebration! Who\'s in for some pre-party karaoke sessions? 🎤', 'Carpool Coordination Thread - Save Gas, Make Friends', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'carpool-coordination-thread-save-gas-make-friends', '', '', '2025-06-13 16:00:08', '2025-06-13 16:00:08', '', 228, '/forums/topic/carpool-coordination-thread-save-gas-make-friends/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2025-06-13 16:17:43', '2025-06-13 16:17:43', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Privacy Policy &amp; Beach Party Guidelines</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> When the sun hits just right<br><strong>Last Updated:</strong> Every time someone asks \"What time should I arrive?\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Data We Collect</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Personal Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We collect your name, embarrassing stories about Alex, and your ability to play beach volleyball (spoiler: most of you can\'t). We also track how many times you\'ve asked \"What should I bring?\" despite reading the FAQ seventeen times.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beach Behavior Analytics</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our advanced monitoring systems (Emily with a clipboard) will be tracking:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Number of times you reapply sunscreen (correlation with lobster-like appearance)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Dance move quality during the evening festivities</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Ability to keep sand out of your food (impossible, we know)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Frequency of \"remember when we were in college\" stories</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Photo Documentation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every unflattering mid-chew photo, every \"candid\" shot where you\'re picking something out of your teeth, and definitely that moment when you think no one is looking but Marcus is literally right there with his camera.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How We Use Your Information</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For Party Optimization</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use your dietary preferences to ensure Dallas doesn\'t accidentally grill you a burger when you clearly stated you\'re vegetarian. We also use your transportation info to coordinate rides and minimize the \"I\'m lost\" text messages to Emily.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For Future Blackmail Material</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Any embarrassing moments will be stored indefinitely for use at future birthday parties, wedding speeches, and general weekend entertainment. This includes but is not limited to: your attempt at the limbo, your interpretive dance to \"Baby Shark,\" and that time you confidently stated you \"definitely know how to build a sandcastle.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For Social Media Shenanigans</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photos may appear on various social media platforms with captions ranging from sweet birthday messages to \"LOL look at this absolute legend trying to spike a volleyball.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Your Rights</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Right to Be Forgotten</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sorry, once you do something embarrassing at Alex\'s party, it becomes part of the permanent record. This is non-negotiable and will be referenced at every future gathering.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Right to Data Portability</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You have the right to take home leftover cake, sandy flip-flops, and approximately 47 new inside jokes that won\'t make sense to anyone who wasn\'t there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Right to Object</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You may object to being assigned to Agnes\'s volleyball team, but your objections will be overruled by the official party democracy (aka Emily\'s clipboard).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cookies Policy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use cookies (the chocolate chip kind) and other tracking technologies (Marcus\'s camera) to enhance your beach party experience. By attending this party, you consent to consuming way too much sugar and having every moment documented for posterity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Data Retention</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will retain your party participation data until:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Alex stops talking about how awesome his 25th birthday was (never)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The group chat stops sending memes from the party (also never)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Someone else does something more embarrassing (unlikely but possible)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Third-Party Sharing</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your information may be shared with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Future party planners who need to know your dietary restrictions</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Alex\'s mom, who will definitely ask Emily for all the photos</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The local seagull population, who seem very interested in your sandwich choices</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Security Measures</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We protect your data using state-of-the-art security measures including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Emily\'s color-coded spreadsheets (military-grade organization)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Dallas\'s protective stance around the grill (no unauthorized access to burgers)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Sofia\'s ability to distract people with impromptu dance performances</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Changes to This Policy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We reserve the right to update this policy whenever someone does something so ridiculous that it requires new categories of data collection. You will be notified of changes via the group chat, probably at 2 AM when someone remembers something funny that happened.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contact Information</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, your data rights, or why we have 47 photos of you trying to eat a s\'more without getting marshmallow in your hair, please contact:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Emily (Party Data Controller)</strong><br>Email: emily.party.planner@beachparty.demo<br>Phone: 888-888-8888<br>Office Hours: 24/7 during party week, because someone always needs something</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>By checking \"I agree to Sample Page,\" you acknowledge that you\'ve read this entire policy, laughed at least three times, and are fully prepared to have the best time at Alex\'s 25th birthday beach extravaganza. You also agree that Alex deserves an absolutely amazing birthday celebration and that you\'ll do everything in your power to make that happen.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Remember: This is a demo website for showcasing WordPress community features. No real data is collected, no real privacy policies apply, and no real marshmallows were harmed in the making of this page.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-06-13 16:17:43', '2025-06-13 16:17:43', '', 125, '/?p=301', 