-daytime-photo-1056497/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/people-running-near-seashore-at-daytime-photo-1056497/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Kindel Media: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-friends-clinking-beer-bottles-7148673/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-friends-clinking-beer-bottles-7148673/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Nathan Cowley: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/closeup-photography-of-sand-1151282/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/closeup-photography-of-sand-1151282/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@vidarnm?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Vidar Nordli-Mathisen</a> on<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/group-of-people-playing-on-beach-AvnXCFX25GA?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Unsplash</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@vidarnm?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> </a><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/es/@ddography?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\">Deniz Demirci</a> on<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/es/fotos/un-grupo-de-personas-sentadas-alrededor-de-una-mesa-FY8Y4bIQyWo?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Unsplash</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@olukai?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Mel Z</a> on<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/a-person-sitting-on-a-beach-next-to-a-campfire-7tQKg4tWaA0?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Unsplash</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@odmln?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Oliver Dumoulin</a> on<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/man-and-woman-near-pool-h2JEHnQm83c?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Unsplash</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@jakobowens1?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Jakob Owens</a> on<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/man-sitting-on-chair-underwater-with-floating-bottles-qoFQxxuk3QY?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Unsplash</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@luwadlinbosman?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Luwadlin Bosman</a> on<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/a-group-of-people-sitting-on-top-of-a-sandy-beach-ZebNoJHeoII?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash\"> Unsplash</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Other images on the site</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Belle Co: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/silhouette-photography-of-group-of-people-jumping-during-golden-time-1000445/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/silhouette-photography-of-group-of-people-jumping-during-golden-time-1000445/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Pixabay: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/brown-wooden-bridge-237272/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/brown-wooden-bridge-237272/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by tre\'s visualz: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-people-at-the-beach-11113771/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-people-at-the-beach-11113771/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About This Site', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '314-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-07-04 17:05:18', '2025-07-04 17:05:18', '', 314, '/?p=318', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(319, 1, '2025-07-04 17:08:14', '2025-07-04 17:08:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Building Cozy Communities That Are Truly Ours</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This beach party website isn\'t just about celebrating Alex\'s 25th birthday. It\'s a showcase of what\'s possible when you combine the power of WordPress with the warmth of genuine community connection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What You\'re Looking At</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This demo site demonstrates how WordPress, paired with plugins like bbPress and BuddyPress, can create intimate, engaging online spaces that feel more like a close-knit friend group than a massive social network. Every feature you see here (from the guest profiles and forum discussions to the event coordination and photo sharing) represents tools that real communities can use to bring people together.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Magic Behind the Scenes</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\">WordPress Core</a></strong>: The foundation that makes everything possible, providing flexibility and reliability for communities of any size.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://bbpress.org/\">bbPress</a></strong>: Powers our forum system where Agnes coordinates volleyball teams, Marcus shares photography tips, and Sofia gets everyone excited about dancing under the stars.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://buddypress.org/\">BuddyPress</a></strong>: Creates the member profiles and social features that let Dallas showcase his BBQ expertise and Emily coordinate all the party logistics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Open Source Customizations</strong>: We\'ve built on WordPress\'s Twenty Twenty-Four theme with a few thoughtful design tweaks and carefully selected plugins that transform standard community tools into something that feels personal and inviting. Everything we\'ve created is open source and ready for you to use. Including the “Community Tags” plugin we created for this project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get Started with Our Blueprint</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can read all about the technical implementation details on our dedicated page, where you can also download a complete WordPress blueprint of this site to use as a starting point for your own community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why \"Cozy Communities\" Matter</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In a world of algorithm-driven feeds and endless scrolling, there\'s something powerful about creating spaces where:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Every member has a voice and a story</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Conversations have context and continuity</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>People actually know each other\'s names (and dietary preferences!)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Shared experiences create lasting connections</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What This Could Be for You</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Imagine using these same tools to create:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Neighborhood Groups</strong>: Coordinate block parties, share local recommendations, and build real relationships with people who live nearby</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Hobby Communities</strong>: Whether it\'s book clubs, hiking groups, or crafting circles, create spaces where enthusiasts can truly connect</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Event Coordination</strong>: From family reunions to professional meetups, give your gatherings the digital foundation they deserve</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Learning Circles</strong>: Study groups, skill shares, and educational communities that feel supportive rather than competitive</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Support Networks</strong>: Safe spaces where people can share experiences, offer help, and build genuine connections</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Philosophy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe the best online communities feel less like social media and more like gathering around a kitchen table. They\'re places where:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Quality conversations matter more than viral content</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Members support each other\'s goals and celebrate wins together</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Inside jokes develop naturally and memories are made</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Everyone feels welcome, valued, and heard</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ready to Build Your Own?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This Alex\'s birthday party demo shows just one way to bring people together online. Your cozy community could look completely different – and that\'s exactly the point. WordPress gives you the foundation, these community plugins provide the features, and your unique vision creates the magic.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether you\'re organizing a monthly game night, building a local artist collective, or creating a space for new parents to connect, the tools exist to make something beautiful and meaningful.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Demo Team</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This showcase was lovingly crafted by the <a href=\"https://specialprojects.automattic.com/\">Automattic Special Projects team</a> to demonstrate the incredible potential of WordPress for community building. Every guest profile, forum post, and party detail was designed to show how technology can enhance rather than replace genuine human connection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Want to explore what\'s possible for your own community? Start with <a href=\"https://wordpress.com/\">WordPress</a>, add some community-focused plugins, sprinkle in your unique vision, and watch something wonderful grow.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"photo-credits\">Photo Credits</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The beautiful images throughout this demo site come from the talented photography community at <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com\">Pexels</a>, <a href=\"https://unsplash.com\">Unsplash</a>, and <a href=\"https://openverse.org/\">OpenVerse</a>. We\'re grateful to these photographers who make their work freely available, enabling projects like ours to showcase the warmth and connection that cozy communities can create.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All photos are used under their respective Creative Commons licenses. Here\'s the list of original images, with the link where you can find them and their photographer credits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Images on the <a href=\"/\">Homepage</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Bayu jefri: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/silhouette-of-people-by-the-seashore-1387037/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/silhouette-of-people-by-the-seashore-1387037/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Nubia Navarro (nubikini): <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/yellow-van-die-cast-386025/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/yellow-van-die-cast-386025/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Quang Nguyen Vinh: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/wicker-hanging-egg-chair-on-picturesque-seaside-3355734/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/wicker-hanging-egg-chair-on-picturesque-seaside-3355734/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Askar Abayev: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-friends-sitting-behind-a-bonfire-5638829/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-friends-sitting-behind-a-bonfire-5638829/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Images on the <a href=\"/itinerary/\">Itinerary Page</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Burst: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-people-doing-cheers-544961/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-people-doing-cheers-544961/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Leung Kwok Tung Ktleung: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/smiling-and-laughing-girls-covered-in-chalk-15855079/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/smiling-and-laughing-girls-covered-in-chalk-15855079/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Nothing Ahead: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/vintage-analog-camera-pentax-on-the-sand-8726574/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/vintage-analog-camera-pentax-on-the-sand-8726574/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Umut Sarıalan: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/a-romantic-table-setting-on-the-pier-in-the-evening-17461431/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/a-romantic-table-setting-on-the-pier-in-the-evening-17461431/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Kindel Media: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-friends-sitting-in-front-of-fire-pit-7148995/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/group-of-friends-sitting-in-front-of-fire-pit-7148995/</a> Photo by Hoàng Tiến Việt: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/fireworks-over-the-ho-chi-minh-city-in-vietnam-19720549/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/fireworks-over-the-ho-chi-minh-city-in-vietnam-19720549/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Luciann Photography: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/cocktails-neon-signage-3566120/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/cocktails-neon-signage-3566120/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Images on the <a href=\"/community-gallery/\">Community Gallery</a></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Vincent Gerbouin: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/man-with-floater-1188470/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/man-with-floater-1188470/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Jill Wellington: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/silhouette-photography-of-jump-shot-of-two-persons-40815/\">https://www.pexels.com/photo/silhouette-photography-of-jump-shot-of-two-persons-40815/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photo by Oliver Sjöström: <a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/people-run