(353, 5, '2025-08-15 16:09:10', '2025-08-15 16:09:10', 'Hey everyone! 🚗\n\nI\'m driving my pickup truck from the west side and I\'ve got room for 2 passengers, plus plenty of space in the truck bed for anyone\'s beach gear, coolers, or party supplies that won\'t fit in their own cars.\n\nEmily, smart thinking on the early departure time! I was planning to head out around 12:00 PM since I\'m bringing all the grilling equipment and want to get the setup started early. If anyone wants to ride with me, fair warning: my truck bed will be loaded with BBQ gear, so it\'s going to smell like charcoal and my secret spice blend the whole ride 😂\n\nAlso volunteering my truck for any last-minute supply runs or if anyone needs help transporting bigger items to the beach. Just let me know!\n\nAgnes, save me some of those cookies - I\'ll trade you some perfectly grilled burgers for them! 🍪🍔', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '353', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:09:10', '2025-08-15 16:09:10', '', 261, '/forums/reply/353/', 2, 'reply', '', 0),
(354, 19, '2025-08-15 16:11:32', '2025-08-15 16:11:32', 'OMG you guys are amazing! 💕🚗\n\nI was planning to take the bus but honestly, a carpool sounds SO much better! I\'m coming from the east side (near the metro station) and would love to catch a ride with anyone heading that direction.\n\nI promise I\'m the best carpool entertainment - I\'ve got the ultimate road trip playlist ready (think feel-good classics mixed with some guilty pleasure pop), and I\'m basically a human energy drink so I\'ll keep everyone hyped for the party! Plus I can navigate like nobody\'s business if needed 📱\n\nDallas, your truck sounds perfect if you\'re going anywhere near the east side! I don\'t mind riding with the BBQ gear - honestly, arriving at the party smelling like your secret spice blend sounds like a bonus 😂\n\nI can pitch in for gas obviously, and I\'ll bring extra snacks for the road! Fair warning though: I WILL try to start a car karaoke session. It\'s basically mandatory road trip behavior! 🎵\n\nAnyone else need a ride from the east side? We could make this a whole convoy situation! ✨', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '354', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:11:32', '2025-08-15 16:11:32', '', 261, '/forums/reply/354/', 3, 'reply', '', 0),
(355, 1, '2025-08-15 16:12:36', '2025-08-15 16:12:36', '<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"bottom\",\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-bottom\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"bottom\",\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"dimensions\":{\"minHeight\":\"\"},\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fit\",\"flexSize\":null}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:site-logo {\"width\":20,\"shouldSyncIcon\":true,\"style\":{\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fit\",\"flexSize\":null}}} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:site-title {\"level\":0,\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:site-tagline {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"bottom\",\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-bottom\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"dimensions\":{\"minHeight\":\"\"},\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fit\",\"flexSize\":null}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"right\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"/about-this-site/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"314\">About this Site</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"/sample-page/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"125\">Policy &amp; Beach Party Guidelines</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"wide\",\"