(356, 18, '2025-08-15 16:22:52', '2025-08-15 16:22:52', 'This is AMAZING and I am absolutely here for it! 📸✨\n\nLeilani, your organizational skills are legendary! And Emily, those childhood videos sound like pure GOLD - I\'m dying to see this bathtub Broadway performance 😂\n\nI\'m volunteering for multiple roles here:\n\n<ol>\n	<li><strong>Official Reaction Photographer</strong> - I\'ll discreetly position myself to capture Alex\'s face during the video montage AND the slideshow. We need to document every single emotion!</li>\n\n	<li><strong>Technical Support</strong> - I can help with the projection setup for the bonfire slideshow and make sure the video montage plays smoothly during dinner</li>\n\n	<li><strong>Contributing Evidence </strong>- I have some great hiking photos of Alex from our adventures, including that time they got so excited about reaching a summit that they did a victory dance on a rock (it\'s adorable and definitely slideshow-worthy)</li>\n\n</ol>\n\nEmily, YES to filming the reaction! I\'ll set up my camera on a tripod to get the wide shot while someone else can get close-ups with their phone. We need this from every angle!\n\nAlso uploading to the shared folder tonight. Alex is going to be such an emotional mess, and it\'s going to be BEAUTIFUL! 🥺📷\n\nThis party is going to be legendary!\n', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '356', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:22:52', '2025-08-15 16:22:52', '', 257, '/forums/reply/356/', 2, 'reply', '', 0),
(357, 19, '2025-08-15 16:27:25', '2025-08-15 16:27:25', 'We need the perfect soundtrack for Alex\'s beach party! Whether it\'s chill vibes for welcome drinks, pump-up songs for beach games, or sunset dinner ambiance, drop your music suggestions here. Let\'s create playlists that\'ll make this celebration absolutely unforgettable!', 'Best Beach Playlist Suggestions - Drop Your Summer Jams', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'best-beach-playlist-suggestions-drop-your-summer-jams', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:27:25', '2025-08-15 16:27:25', '', 228, '/forums/topic/best-beach-playlist-suggestions-drop-your-summer-jams/', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
(358, 19, '2025-08-15 16:35:47', '2025-08-15 16:35:47', '   Okay party people, it\'s MUSIC TIME! 🎵✨\n\n   I\'ve been working on the ultimate beach party soundtrack and I need ALL your input! We need different vibes for different parts of the day, so here\'s what I\'m thinking:\n\n   <strong>Welcome Drinks - Chill but Happy:</strong>\n   <ul>\n     <li>\"Levitating\" - Dua Lipa (perfect beach energy!)</li>\n     <li>\"As It Was\" - Harry Styles (everyone knows this one)</li>\n     <li>\"Anti-Hero\" - Taylor Swift (because why not?)</li>\n   </ul>\n\n   <strong>Beach Games - High Energy:</strong>\n   <ul>\n     <li>\"Uptown Funk\" - Bruno Mars (classic crowd pleaser)</li>\n     <li>\"Good 4 U\" - Olivia Rodrigo (gets everyone hyped)</li>\n     <li>\"Heat Waves\" - Glass Animals (summer vibes!)</li>\n   </ul>\n\n   <strong>Sunset Dinner - Mellow but Warm:</strong>\n   <ul>\n     <li>\"Golden\" - Harry Styles (literally perfect for sunset)</li>\n     <li>\"Adorn\" - Miguel (smooth and romantic)</li>\n   </ul>\n\n   <strong>Dance Party - ALL THE BANGERS:</strong>\n   <ul>\n     <li>Anything that makes you want to move! This is where I need the most help!</li>\n   </ul>\n\n   Drop your suggestions below! What songs make YOU want to dance like nobody\'s watching? And yes, I\'m absolutely taking requests for throwback hits and guilty pleasure songs!\n\n   Let\'s make Alex\'s 25th have the PERFECT soundtrack! 🎶\n', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '358', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:35:47', '2025-08-15 16:35:47', '', 357, '/forums/reply/358/', 1, 'reply', '', 0),
(359, 11, '2025-08-15 16:36:39', '2025-08-15 16:36:39', 'Hey food squad! 🌮✨\n\nThis coordination is looking incredible already - Dallas, you\'re a legend for taking on all that grilling! And Emily, that condiment setup sounds like heaven!\n\nI\'m jumping in to handle the appetizer and snack situation because let\'s be real, we\'re going to need munchies during those beach games! Here\'s what I\'m bringing:\n\n* Fresh fruit platter (watermelon, pineapple, grapes - perfect for hot beach weather)\n* Chips and guac (homemade guac because I\'m extra like that 🥑)\n* Veggie tray with hummus\n* Those little pinwheel sandwiches that are perfect for grabbing between volleyball sets\n* And my specialty: spicy mango salsa that pairs perfectly with literally everything Dallas is grilling!\n\nI\'m also thinking we might want some late-night munchies for the bonfire crowd? I can throw together a s\'mores kit with all the fixings - graham crackers, chocolate, marshmallows, plus some fun variations like peanut butter cups and strawberries for the fancy s\'mores experience!\n\nQuestion for the group: Should someone coordinate drinks beyond the welcome cocktails? I\'m happy to bring a cooler of sodas, water, and maybe some beer if people want options throughout the day?\n\nThis menu is shaping up to be EPIC! Alex is going to be so spoiled! 🎉', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '359', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:36:39', '2025-08-15 16:36:39', '', 254, '/forums/reply/359/', 2, 'reply', '', 0),
(360, 13, '2025-08-15 16:37:27', '2025-08-15 16:37:27', 'Sofia, YES! I am SO here for this! 🎵\n\nI\'ve been curating the perfect beach party playlist in my head for weeks! Here are my contributions:\n\n<strong>Welcome Drinks Vibes:</strong>\n<ul>\n <li>\"Watermelon Sugar\" - Harry Styles (peak summer energy)</li>\n <li>\"Blinding Lights\" - The Weeknd (gets everyone moving)</li>\n <li>\"Flowers\" - Miley Cyrus (empowering and fun!)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<strong>Beach Games Pump-Up:</strong>\n<ul>\n <li>\"Can\'t Stop the Feeling\" - Justin Timberlake (impossible not to smile)</li>\n <li>\"Sunflower\" - Post Malone (chill but upbeat)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<strong>Sunset Dinner Chill:</strong>\n<ul>\n <li>\"Stay\" - Rihanna (classic and not too distracting from conversation)</li>\n <li>\"Ocean Eyes\" - Billie Eilish (dreamy sunset vibes)</li>\n</ul>\n\nFair warning: I may have included like 47 Taylor Swift songs in my original draft, but I narrowed it down to the essentials 😂\n\nAlso voting for at least ONE throwback slow song for when we inevitably get sentimental during dinner! What do you think?', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '360', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:37:27', '2025-08-15 16:37:27', '', 357, '/forums/reply/360/', 2, 'reply', '', 0),
(361, 11, '2025-08-15 16:38:46', '2025-08-15 16:38:46', 'This is my JAM! 🎸✨ (Literally, music is my thing)\n\nSofia, your playlist structure is perfect! I\'m adding some acoustic and indie vibes to balance out the energy:\n\n<strong>Welcome Drinks - Chill Acoustic:</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>\"Riptide\" - Vance Joy (perfect beach song)</li>\n  <li>\"Better Days\" - OneRepublic (good vibes only)</li>\n  <li>\"Budapest\" - George Ezra (everyone loves this one)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<strong>Sunset Dinner - Soulful &amp; Warm:</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>\"Banana Pancakes\" - Jack Johnson (ultimate chill)</li>\n  <li>\"Three Little Birds\" - Bob Marley (everything\'s gonna be alright)</li>\n  <li>\"Here Comes the Sun\" - The Beatles (classic and perfect timing)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<strong>Dance Party - Throwback Gold:</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>\"Mr. Brightside\" - The Killers (EVERYONE will sing along)</li>\n  <li>\"Don\'t Stop Believin\'\" - Journey (mandatory group sing-along)</li>\n</ul>\n\nAgnes, YES to sentimental slow songs! I vote for \"Wonderwall\" during bonfire time - I can play it live on guitar if people want that acoustic moment 🔥🎶\n\nAlex is going to love this soundtrack!', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '361', '', '', '2025-08-15 16:38:46', '2025-08-15 16:38:46', '', 357, '/forums/reply/361/', 3, 'reply', '', 0),
